NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The priorities for responders are to bid the 4-card major if they have one, to bid 1D if they don't have 4-card major and only to bid 1N if they do not have any other bid. Of course we are talking when the responder has a minimum hand.|
