NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|A. Here when you run the clubs, it is likely one of the defenders will discard a diamond, so you should guard against the other defender having 4 diamonds.|
PG| ***** 118 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|B. Unlike the previous hand with the spade play, there are 2 equally good ways to play the diamond suit, depending on who you think is more likely to have started with 4 diamonds. That is because, unlike the previous spade hand, on this hand declarer has both the @D10 and @D9. |
